  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A study of the efficacy and tolerability of two different ketogenic diets in children with
      drug resistant epilepsy; children resistant to at least two drugs randomised to reveive diet
      after baseline or after further 3m control period; in addition randomised to either MCT or
      classical ketogenic diet.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
